Poland: Signing of the Second Peace of Thorn (Toruń) concludes the Thirteen Years' War
Indonesia: Singhawikramawardhana, succeeds Girishawardhana as ruler of Majapahit.
Belgium: Dinant sacked by the forces of Philip the Good, commanded by Charles the Bold
Albania: The Albanians, led by Skanderbeg, began the defense of Krujë against massive Ottoman armies.
